narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I appreciated the way that the syllabus drew on texts from a wide range of disciplines and historical moments of theorizing diaspora. If anything, I would have appreciated longer readings to have additional material to engage with and to have the opportunity to more thoroughly engage the thinkers that we read.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would recommend the course to any student whose research intersects with black diaspora studies, whether they were in an art program or another program.
